rComments: Lots of reading, but awesome reading list! Allows for class interaction. Greet interpretations. Glad I took this! Would love to take another course with her .

I'm so happy I took this class. Dr. Sheikh is a great prof all around. Amazing reading list, broke up lectures with class discussions, fair marker (lets you know what/how you will be tested--amazing final exam!), easy to talk to, posts notes, clearly has a lot of passion for it all. Brought out important aspects of the novels I hadn't considered.
